article.headline: Clarke, Stephenson-Moore lead Stony Brook over Army 78-74 in OT

images.name: Stony Brook Seawolves vs. Army Black Knights: Full Highlights
images.caption: Stony Brook Seawolves vs. Army Black Knights: Full Highlights

article.linkText: Clarke, Stephenson-Moore lead Stony Brook over Army 78-74 in OT
article.story: WEST POINT, N.Y. -- — Aaron Clarke had 21 points off the bench, Tyler Stephenson-Moore scored eight in overtime and Stony Brook beat Army 78-74 on Sunday. Clarke shot 5 for 10 (4 for 6 from 3-point range) and 7 of 8 from the free-throw line for the Seawolves (6-5). Keenan Fitzmorris scored 15 points while finishing 7 of 11 from the floor, adding six rebounds. Stephenson-Moore scored 11. Josh Scovens finished with 31 points, seven assists and four steals for the Black Knights (2-9). Army also got 16 points from TJ Small. In addition, Ryan Curry finished with 10 points, six rebounds and seven assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
